WEBVTT

00:02:59.258 --> 00:03:04.288
and variations in the bacteria species
that live in our digestive systems.

00:03:04.288 --> 00:03:09.255
No matter the cause, obesity is
an escalating global epidemic.

00:03:09.255 --> 00:03:12.790
It substantially raises the probability
of diseases,

00:03:12.790 --> 00:03:14.136
like diabetes,

00:03:14.136 --> 00:03:15.254
heart disease,

00:03:15.254 --> 00:03:16.817
stroke,

00:03:16.817 --> 00:03:18.322
high blood pressure,

00:03:18.322 --> 00:03:19.974
and cancer.

00:03:19.974 --> 00:03:24.474
It affects virtually all ages, genders,
and socioeconomic groups

00:03:24.474 --> 00:03:27.512
in both developed 
and developing countries.

